{"tid":2126634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問IG貼光時 袁嘉蔚刪相","createTime":"2020-07-27T03:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T03:28:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1330b9849ea0e41fd947cde2fee1225a206fbc3c","tid":2126634,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/WBDKGLQI3RIR3AH4VUAYQXWOTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FWBDKGLQI3RIR3AH4VUAYQXWOTI%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=b73240fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FWBDKGLQI3RIR3AH4VUAYQXWOTI%2F&h=89185157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/WBDKGLQI3RIR3AH4VUAYQXWOTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n被問IG貼光時 袁嘉蔚刪相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X_XNIiUAIwrZUXQ_LYgsofXVsiU=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I3YUDPMA5GC7DIRDNJOOUFEN4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX_XNIiUAIwrZUXQ_LYgsofXVsiU%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI3YUDPMA5GC7DIRDNJOOUFEN4A.jpg&h=8aa77d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁嘉蔚<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。。。。其中參選港島袁嘉蔚昨回覆港島區選舉主任黃智華，強調被問及有關「光復香港 時代革命」圖片早在今年1月上載，港府發聲明指涉違法後未有再上載，不同意是「持續展示」，但為免參選資格受影響，已暫時將相片刪除。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公民黨四人斥提問越權<br />\n<br />\n張崑陽引葉劉訪美辯護<br />\n<br />\n梁晃維也收到黃智華查詢，他回覆指無意請求美國政府實施制裁，解釋「義無反顧的反對《國安法》」，不代表他原則上反對港版國安法，只是認為其制訂過程及內容有值得商榷地方。<br />\n<br />\n前記者何桂藍回覆選舉主任楊蕙心有關反對港版國安法提問時指，由人大常委會通過並列入《基本法》附件三、再由特區宣佈生效港版國安法，多處牴觸《基本法》條文，因此反對港版國安法單方面頒佈及執行。張崑陽亦回覆查詢，。。。。。。。。。。。。。早前表明「義無反顧的反對國安法」是指反對人大常委會單次政治決定形式，非質疑人大常委會的憲制權力。"},{"pid":"a979440b550730be71ae492c3a7d8e056bc05504","tid":2126634,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"入左閘先算<br />\ndel晒所有野去"}]}